## Frontend changes

### Design context (once per project)
- `.impeccable.md` missing ā†’ JARVIS invokes skill `impeccable teach` before ANY design task
- `.impeccable.md` exists ā†’ all design skills read it automatically

### Planning (before code)
- New feature with UX decisions ā†’ **first** skill `shape`, then implementation
- Simple component ā†’ `/frontend-design`

### Implementation
- Complex UI ā†’ skill `impeccable craft`
- Utility component ā†’ `/frontend-design`

### Refinement (as needed)
- Typography feels generic ā†’ skill `typeset`
- Colors flat ā†’ skill `colorize`
- Need animation ā†’ skill `animate`
- Agency-tier polish ā†’ skill `high-end-visual-design`

### Audit
- Full (a11y + perf + tokens) ā†’ skill `audit`
- Quick: `/css-audit`, `/responsive-check`

### Always
- `*.tsx` with `t()`/`ts()` ā†’ `/i18n-sync`
- New color 3+ times ā†’ `/theme-token`
- Final polish ā†’ skill `polish`
- Bug screenshot ā†’ `/screenshot-diff` ā†’ skill `polish`
